A History of Western Art
Henry Holt and Company | 1953 | ISBN: N/A | English | 998 pages | PDF | 118 MB

This book is an attempt to provide the reader with an introduction to the study of the visual arts. The chief problem has been one of space. How, in a few hundred pages, can one cover a field with a present literature so vast that no single scholar can be physically capable of reading it all?
